Beyond Flavours,Mudit,"I have been at this place for dinner a few days back. The ambience was good. The restaurant was almost half occupied. We immediately got a table. But then waited for 10 mins to get water and menu, that too after a few reminders. We ordered a few starters, main course items and mock drinks. Only the starters could be served in 30 mins. There was no sign of mock drinks! We noticed similar service issues on other tables. Noticed guests literally shouting on the staff.

The food was just average. Dishes were not prepared well, at least when compared to 4.1 rating on Zomato.

We finally decided to just have starters, and hop onto another restaurant for rest of the meal!",2.0,5/12/2019 8:37,i have been at this place for dinner a few days back the ambience was good the restaurant was almost half occupied we immediately got a table but then waited for mins to get water and menu that too after a few reminders we ordered a few starters main course items and mock drinks only the starters could be served in mins there was no sign of mock drinks we noticed similar service issues on other tables noticed guests literally shouting on the staff the food was just average dishes were not prepared well at least when compared to rating on zomato we finally decided to just have starters and hop onto another restaurant for rest of the meal,673,2,119
Beyond Flavours,Vignesh Rk,"I would like to introduce this restaurant to a new ingredient called salt. If you add that yo your food, it would taste way better. So basically none of the food we ordered had salt. We ordered Fries, panko mozzarella sticks, Tomato cream soup, panner65 & ""Italian"" Nachos. Not sure how that was nachos or italian. They basically bought a pack of dorittos and added mozarella cheese on top. The beans were not baked at all, and the entire dish was cold except for the plate that it was brought in. Pretty sure they just dumped the items and stashed it inside a microwave. The paneer 65 was horrendous. Might as well called it garlic 65 with no salt. Next was the mozarella sticks, which was again cold and no salt. The only decent item that we got was the fries and the soup. Thanks to gid we didnt order any main course. All these came up to 1300 and odd. Thanks to Zomato Gold, our price went down. This place is way too expensive for the quality of food they serve. And talking about the restaurant in general, the place looks decent but there are stoves stashed under tables and seats and plants kept at inconvenient spots. They really need to clean up more.",1.0,5/11/2019 10:06,i would like to introduce this restaurant to a new ingredient called salt if you add that yo your food it would taste way better so basically none of the food we ordered had salt we ordered fries panko mozzarella sticks tomato cream soup panner italian nachos not sure how that was nachos or italian they basically bought a pack of dorittos and added mozarella cheese on top the beans were not baked at all and the entire dish was cold except for the plate that it was brought in pretty sure they just dumped the items and stashed it inside a microwave the paneer was horrendous might as well called it garlic with no salt next was the mozarella sticks which was again cold and no salt the only decent item that we got was the fries and the soup thanks to gid we didnt order any main course all these came up to and odd thanks to zomato gold our price went down this place is way too expensive for the quality of food they serve and talking about the restaurant in general the place looks decent but there are stoves stashed under tables and seats and plants kept at inconvenient spots they really need to clean up more,1162,2,211
