Cascade - Radisson Hyderabad Hitec City,Anand Radhakrishnan,"Came here for some late night dinner and my experience can be termed ""Pathetic"" to say the least. They do not believe in serving a glass of water unless specifically asked for after 20 minutes of being there. The smell of the cleaning liquid was so strong that i lost my appetite and to top it gave me a splitting headache. Although they claim it to be open 24 hours, they apparently start cleaning up the place around midnight. Customers be damned! I asked them to pack up the food because there was no way i was going to eat from there bearing the mind numbing smell. After the food parcel was given, they wouldn't give me the cheque unless of course, again specifically asked for. The kind of experience you would expect from a place that serves biryani for Rs 50 and not Rs 800!! Endured the 40 minutes of torture, grabbed the take-away and left.",1.0,5/14/2017 1:10,came here for some late night dinner and my experience can be termed pathetic to say the least they do not believe in serving a glass of water unless specifically asked for after minutes of being there the smell of the cleaning liquid was so strong that i lost my appetite and to top it gave me a splitting headache although they claim it to be open hours they apparently start cleaning up the place around midnight customers be damned i asked them to pack up the food because there was no way i was going to eat from there bearing the mind numbing smell after the food parcel was given they wouldn t give me the cheque unless of course again specifically asked for the kind of experience you would expect from a place that serves biryani for rs and not rs endured the minutes of torture grabbed the take away and left,850,1,154
